      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Replace the M3 Scouts in this Unit with Universal Carriers from (LB112) with the following ratings. You may add a second Universal Carrier per M3 Scout for +1 point each.Arm all Universal Carriers with Boys AT rifles for +1 point for the Unit.MOTIVATIONCONFIDENT4+TransportCounterattack 6TransportRemount 6
SKILLTRAINED4+TransportAssault 6
IS HIT ONAGRESSIVE3+  Universal Carriers have Passengers 2.</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Notes" typeId="75a6-20ee-1c76-640a">Soviet, Unit (Reconaissance Company HQ, Armoured Reconnaissance Platoon)</characteristic>
